Last Of The Summer Wine - Series 29 - Episode 9

Of Passion And Pizza

BBC One - 17 August 2008

Merywn finds himself in love with &#039;Her&#039; at the pizza take-away, but can&#039;t get up the nerve to let her know.
He does, however, have the horrific idea of letting Alvin and Entwistle know in the hopes they can get the relationship started.

The longest running comedy series in the world started out, as many British comedy successes did, with a 1973 episode of the BBC series "Comedy Playhouse".
The basis was simple but complex at the same time. It tells us the stories of three old men, who in all essence couldn&#039;t be more young at heart.
